  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/513610/extras/a92b8572c8fe37bf9eba5a940832ffee.avif?t=1760395901\" width=616 height=108 /></span><br>MadRobot X is an old school shoot 'em up game. You control a robot trying to escape from the laboratory of a mad scientist, and to accomplish this, you'll need the help of GoboGobo, another robot who also wants to escape. The task is not easy; the mad scientist will do anything to prevent anyone from escaping.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pixel art style<br></li><li> Progressive challenge<br></li><li> Power ups<br></li><li> Special skills<br></li><li> 12 Bosses<br></li><li> Bullets, bullets, bullets!<br></li><li> Nightmare Mode<br></li><li> Gameservices Scoreboard<br></li><li> Gamepad support with 2 modes:<br> * Normal: LStick moves the robot, RStick shoots and maneuvers the beam<br> * Classic: LStick moves the robot and maneuvers the beam, buttons shoot<br></li><li> Gameplay adjustments (hitbox, touchscreen, hp recovery, etc...)<br></li><li> The ability to mute, not only the music, but sound effects as well<br></li><li> And much more (like bullets!)</li></ul>",
